00:45:01,288 --> 00:45:06,360
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">Sir, there is also the humanitarian argument.</font></b>

522
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:10,826
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">Should he die for doing the job
