00:49:40,567 --> 00:49:44,371
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">our strongest grounds for reversal...</font></b>

573
00:49:44,471 --> 00:49:46,834
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">are constitutional.</font></b>

574
00:49:48,558 --> 00:49:52,937
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">Our best chance is if the Supreme Court
