00:50:51,716 --> 00:50:54,701
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">I've got her. Upstairs!</font></b>

589
00:50:56,443 --> 00:50:59,613
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">- I sat with my back against the wall, Dad!
