595
00:51:14,694 --> 00:51:16,629
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">Maybe we'll find a description of the car</font></b>

596
00:51:16,729 --> 00:51:19,966
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">- but I don't think it's very likely.
