607
00:51:50,578 --> 00:51:52,614
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">I'm sorry.</font></b>

608
00:52:12,519 --> 00:52:15,280
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">Do you feel that you deserve this, sir?</font></b>

609
00:52:37,210 --> 00:52:41,781
