656
00:56:39,118 --> 00:56:42,188
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">That, Rudolf Abel will never do.</font></b>

657
00:56:42,288 --> 00:56:46,126
<b><font face="Arial Narrow">Shouldn't we, by giving him the full benefit
